pro_course_detail.description:
Planning to take the DELE exam? It is useful to set clear goals and dates to start preparing. We'll work with mock exams, and we’ll focus on your weaker areas, specifically aiming at mastering the contents that your level requires (corresponding to the contents provided by the Cervantes Institute, for A1-C1-levels).

To achieve a positive result, we can carry out periodic and intensive training sessions:

-For you to get acquainted with the format of the exam and work with it;
-Refresh your grammar; 
-Practice reading; and,
-Improve your listening, speaking and writing skills.
